    "## Figure 6 -- Provenance and Artifact Completeness\n",
    "\n",
    "**Paper role (Sec 3.4 / Appendix):** Demonstrates the audit-trail claim: every trial\n",
    "has a complete chain (proposal -> patch -> run -> metric -> decision). 100% provenance\n",
    "on all 495 trials including 135 ResNet failures. This is what makes results\n",
    "reproducible and independently verifiable.\n"
   ]
