    "## Figure 7 -- OpenML Best-Metric Trajectory\n",
    "\n",
    "**Paper role (Sec 4.5):** Demonstrates real performance improvement on real ML tasks.\n",
    "Running best val_AUC is monotone (by the keep rule), and improvement is consistent\n",
